	U-16 cricket
    
	Calcutta: Abhimanyu Easwaran scalped six for 17 as Bengal dismissed Tripura for 98 in a Vijay Merchant Trophy (U-16) match in Siliguri on Tuesday. Earlier Bengal declared at 312 for nine in their first innings. Following on, Tripura were 2/0.  
